Package io.openlineage.client.dataset

Class Naming

java.lang.Object
io.openlineage.client.dataset.Naming
public final class Naming extends Object
Utility class containing dataset naming helpers based on OpenLineage's dataset naming specification.

Each inner class represents naming logic for a specific platform (e.g., BigQuery, AWS Glue), and provides methods to construct valid dataset names and namespaces.
